title: Ranked with people first time in ranked

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: So I am Silver 3, not amazing but still I should not be playing with people who just hit level 30, the wukong was 3/13 and unranked, I am silver 3 why am I playing with him this is crazy.

replies.body:
Hey there,

Silver 3 is around the average MMR for fresh level 30's just entering ranked.

Also this thread would be better suited for the [Gameplay & Strategy](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-strategy) or [Miscellaneous](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous) boards.
